---
import MarketingLayout from '../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';
import CTABanner from '../components/CTABanner.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout title="About Us - Evaluetor" description="A small team in Rotterdam building the contract intelligence platform that enterprises deserve but have never had. Our story, our mission, and why we're different.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <Hero
    tag="Our Story"
    headline='A small team with a <span class="text-primary-600">big bet</span>'
    subheadline="We're building the contract intelligence platform that enterprises deserve but have never had."
    primaryCTA={{ text: 'Talk to the team', href: '/contact' }}
    secondaryCTA={{ text: 'See the product', href: '/product' }}
  />

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <SectionHeading
          tag="The Bet"
          title="Contracts are broken. We're fixing it."
        />
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed -mt-6">
          Here's what's wild: enterprises spend millions negotiating contracts, then file them in a drawer. Nobody reads them. Nobody tracks the obligations. Nobody claims the service credits they're owed. And when something goes wrong, everyone scrambles to find the document.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          We think that's insane. So we built an AI that reads every contract, extracts every obligation, tracks every deadline, and monitors every vendor relationship. Not as a feature bolted onto a document repository — as the core of the product.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story (dark) -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-950">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <SectionHeading
          tag="Why"
          title="Born from frustration"
          dark={true}
        />
        <div class="text-lg text-gray-400 mx-auto text-center leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Years of experience in vendor governance and relationship management revealed a painful truth: enterprises lose millions to contracts they can't track. Legal teams drowning in manual review. Procurement missing SLA breaches. Finance discovering auto-renewals after they've triggered.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">
            Evaluetor was started in Rotterdam with a simple thesis: if AI can read and understand contracts better than any individual person, why are we still doing it manually? So we built a platform that doesn't just store contracts — it understands them.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <SectionHeading
        tag="Our Approach"
        title="Why we're different"
      />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904 9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 3.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-3.09 3.09ZM18.259 8.715 18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 0 0 2.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-2.456 2.456Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">AI-first, not AI-added</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Every competitor bolts AI onto a document repository. We built the AI first, then wrapped the product around it. Eight specialized agents, not one generic model.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Relationships, not just documents</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Contracts define terms. Relationships determine outcomes. We're the only platform that measures how both sides perceive the partnership — not just what the contract says.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-gray-100 text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">European-built, enterprise-ready</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Headquartered in Rotterdam. GDPR-native. Data stays where you need it. No compromises on privacy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who's Behind This -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <SectionHeading
        tag="Behind Evaluetor"
        title="Who's building this"
      />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 shadow-md shadow-primary-500/20">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">S.E.Visser Consultancy B.V.</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-primary-600 font-semibold mt-1">Strategy & Domain Expertise</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">Deep experience in vendor governance, business relationship management, and enterprise contract operations. The domain knowledge and strategic vision behind Evaluetor.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5 shadow-md shadow-primary-500/20">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75 22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3-4.5 16.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Syntegreti Technologies B.V.</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-primary-600 font-semibold mt-1">Engineering & AI</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-3 leading-relaxed">The technical force building the platform. AI-native architecture, multi-agent orchestration, and the engineering that turns domain expertise into working software.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Facts -->
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <SectionHeading
        tag="Company"
        title="Company facts"
      />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500/5 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">2024</div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Founded</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Rotterdam, Netherlands</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500/5 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Rotterdam</div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Headquarters</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">European Union</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500/5 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Contract Intelligence</div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Focus</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">AI-powered analysis and governance</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/60 text-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500/5 to-transparent"></div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Self-funded</div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Backed By</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Independent. Customer-focused.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <CTABanner
    headline="Want to see what we're building?"
    subtext="We'll walk you through a live demo with your own contracts. No slides, no sales pitch."
    buttonText="Talk to us"
    buttonLink="/contact"
  />

</MarketingLayout>
